🛍️ Everyday Transactions

Coffee Shops & Fast Food: Chains like Starbucks and Sheetz accept crypto payments via apps and third-party processors.

Retailers: Companies such as Microsoft and Home Depot are integrating crypto payments for everyday purchases.


✈️ Travel & Luxury

Airlines & Travel: Platforms like Travala.com enable bookings with BTC, ETH, and XRP.

Luxury Goods: High-end car dealerships and real estate developers are accepting crypto for premium products and properties.


🏪 Small Businesses

Payment processors are simplifying crypto adoption for small businesses by converting crypto to fiat instantly, reducing compliance costs.
